event.description:
6-Time Grammy Winner, Taylor Swift, is returning to Toronto, this time taking Rogers Centre with her North American RED TOUR on Friday, June 14 and Saturday, June 15, 2013. The RED TOUR, featuring special guest, Ed Sheeran, will highlight songs from Swift's brand new album, RED, including the hit song "We Are Never Ever Getting Back Together."
